---
import Default from '../../layouts/Default.astro';
---
<Default title="Labs · Harshith Kantamneni" description="Autonomous AI labs running on commodity hardware." current="labs">

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-parallax-layer hero-parallax-layer-1" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="hero-parallax-layer hero-parallax-layer-2" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <span class="index-number">Labs</span>
      <h1 style="max-width: 18ch;">Lab modules.</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        Each lab is a persistent organization: a Director coordinating specialist
        sub-agents, with memory, evaluators, red-team review, and structured artifacts.
        The methodology is published openly, and new labs plug into the same modular
        framework as they come online.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="padding-top: 0;">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="card-grid">

        <a href="/harshithkantamneni.github.io/labs/hive" class="tilt-card">
          <div class="card-inner">
            <span class="status-pill live">Live</span>
            <h3>HIVE Product Lab</h3>
            <p class="meta">Product engineering · active since 2026</p>
            <p>
              Specialist agents for architecture, mobile engineering, code review,
              red team, evaluator, and knowledge management. CI-bound external verdict
              and pre-registered streak falsifiers.
            </p>
            <div class="stack">
              <span>Rust</span><span>Mobile FFI</span><span>Cross-platform</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/harshithkantamneni.github.io/labs/autonomous-research" class="tilt-card">
          <div class="card-inner">
            <span class="status-pill live">Live</span>
            <h3>Autonomous Research Lab</h3>
            <p class="meta">Research operations · active since 2026</p>
            <p>
              Tiered persistent memory, pre-registration discipline, governance ledgers,
              reproducibility gates, honest negative results. Small-model
              experimentation under constrained local compute.
            </p>
            <div class="stack">
              <span>Small models</span><span>Pre-registration</span><span>Tiered memory</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>

        <article class="card" style="opacity: 0.65;">
          <span class="status-pill dormant">In design</span>
          <h3>New module incoming</h3>
          <p class="meta">Pre-launch</p>
          <p>
            A new lab module is currently being designed. More once it has a name
            and a shipped first cycle.
          </p>
        </article>

      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</Default>
